---
import { ClientRouter } from "astro:transitions";
import "../../styles/global.css";
import ProjectDescription from "../../components/ProjectDescription";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <ClientRouter />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Bacanora Sierra Madre</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-foreground">
    <a
      href="/"
      class="fixed left-6 top-6 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-geist shadow-sm transition hover:shadow"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="16"
        height="16"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="lucide lucide-arrow-left-icon lucide-arrow-left"
        ><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"></path><path d="M19 12H5"></path></svg
      >
      <span>Return home</span>
    </a>
    <main
      class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen w-full max-w-4xl flex-col gap-6 px-6 py-24 font-geist"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-3xl font-semibold md:text-5xl"
        transition:name="project-bacanora"
      >
        Bacanora Sierra Madre
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
        Landing Page / February 2026
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/hiiramsan/sierramadre"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex! items-center! gap-2! rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-geist shadow-sm transition hover:shadow"
        >
          <span>Visit the Github</span>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right shrink-0"
            ><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://bacanorasierramadre.vercel.app/"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex! items-center! gap-2! rounded-md border border-neutral-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-geist shadow-sm transition hover:shadow"
        >
          <span>Visit project</span>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right shrink-0"
            ><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/sierramadre.png"
        alt="Project preview"
        class="w-150 rounded-md"
      />
      <ProjectDescription
        client:load
        version1={[
          "Built with Astro and Tailwind, this landing page gives Bacanora Sierra Madre a modern digital presence and highlights the product story.",
          "My goal was to keep the layout clean and premium with strong typography, large imagery, and clear sections.",
          "I love designing landing pages and I am looking for the next challenge to keep improving and deliver the best work.",
        ]}
        version2={[
          "I am incredibly humbled to announce the successful digital transformation of Sierra Madre, a prestige heritage brand that I have officially transitioned into the high-stakes world of the 4.0 economy. By architecting a bespoke, cloud-optimized landing environment using an edge-first component model and a utility-first styling paradigm, I have effectively bridged the gap between ancestral artisanal craftsmanship and the ultra-modern consumer interface.",
          "This initiative was never just about a 'web presence', it was a rigorous exercise in Premium Visual Storytelling and Global Brand Equity Localization. I deliberately curated a high-fidelity, minimalist layout anchored by authoritative typography and expansive imagery to maximize emotional engagement and drive stakeholder resonance. My focus was on establishing a 'digital distillery' where the product’s narrative isn't just viewed, but experienced through a friction-less, high-conversion UI.",
          "As a devoted practitioner of Visual Excellence and Digital Architecture, I am now actively scouting for my next high-impact partnership. I am ready to leverage my unique design-thinking methodology to disrupt static industries and deliver world-class, market-ready digital assets that push the absolute boundaries of the modern web.",
          "#HeritageDisruption #VisualCapital #DigitalDistillation #BrandEvolution #UIArchitect #ArtisanalInnovation #HighPerformanceDesign"
        ]}
      />
      
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
